abc.parser
Class AbcHeadersParser

java.lang.Object
  abc.parser.AbcParserAbstract
      abc.parser.AbcFileParser
          abc.parser.AbcHeadersParser
public class AbcHeadersParser
extends AbcFileParser

This class provides parser instances that reduce the parsing scope to tunes headers (music is excluded). This results in a much faster parsing than parsing the whole tunes and enables you to build up tunes indexes fastly.
Just invoke the usual methods #parseFile(File abcFile) or #parseFile(Reader abcCharStream) and you'll get in return instances of Tune without any Score part.
